@startuml seq-12-shop-list
' 序列图12：商城浏览商品
title 商城浏览商品序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "shop.js" as Front
participant "ProductController" as Ctrl
participant "ProductService" as Svc
participant "ProductMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 打开商城,点击分类tab(全部/家具/木料/工具/课程)
Front -> Ctrl: GET /api/product/list?categoryId=0
Ctrl -> Svc: list(categoryId)
Svc -> Mapper: selectByCategory(categoryId)
Mapper -> DB: SELECT * FROM product WHERE category_id=? OR 0=?
DB --> Mapper: List<Product>
Mapper --> Svc: List<Product>
Svc --> Ctrl: List<Product>
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:List}
Front -> Front: _fixUrl()拼接图片baseUrl
Front --> User: 渲染商品瀑布流

@enduml
